meta.prompt: A captivating image of a dark, eerie ballerina robot, imbued with a cosmic horror theme. The robot stands gracefully in a dramatic pose, its body illuminated by dim, otherworldly light, casting elongated shadows. Its intricate design combines steampunk and dark fantasy elements, with a worn, organic appearance to its skirt that evokes decay and surrealism. Surrounding the robot is a mysterious, mechanical background that adds to the haunting atmosphere. The combination of these elements creates a striking visual narrative of a haunting, otherworldly dancer, drawing the viewer into a world of enigmatic beauty and chilling wonder.

A close-up of a Middle Eastern woman wearing a luxurious pink satin hijab, intricately embroidered with silver and pink jewels. Her light green eyes, framed by perfectly shaped brows and accentuated by dark eyeliner, are captivating. The softly blurred background, with warm bokeh lights, enhances the elegance and mystique of her gaze.

Her characteristics are Smooth, flawless tanned skin with a natural glow. Refined, elegant nose with a delicate bridge.Delicate, minimal makeup emphasizing her natural beauty.Soft, warm-toned eyeshadow complementing her eye color.

Pink satin hijab with intricate silver embroidery along the edges. Delicate veil adorned with tiny, dangling pink gemstones. Jeweled headpiece with a central gem resting on her forehead. Subtle metallic accents in the embroidery, reflecting light.
Long, flowing sleeves with delicate lace trimming. Soft, sheer layer of fabric over the satin, adding dimension. long sleeves past wrist.

Her right hand lightly touches the edge of her veil near her cheek, eyes looking thoughtfully into the distance.

The rustic wooden house setting is illuminated by dramatic, high-contrast lighting, creating a moody, mysterious atmosphere. Black flowers and wilted blooms add to the textured, haunting beauty of the scene.

The woman turns her head quickly to one side, as if something caught her attention.
A small lion cub sleeps on a robotic vacuum cleaner on a big carpet in the living room.
